translate spanish izzyarcadedatestart_a324d7e5:

    # gl "So we're going to an arcade? I haven't played any arcade games in forever."
    gl "¿Así que vamos a una sala de juegos? Hace una eternidad que no juego a nada en una sala de juegos."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/IzzyDates/izzyarcadedate.rpy:29
translate spanish izzyarcadedatestart_d41d8cd9:

    # voice 'voices/izzy_whatsup.mp3'
    voice 'voices/izzy_whatsup.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Izzy/IzzyDates/izzyarcadedate.rpy:30
translate spanish izzyarcadedatestart_515d2991:

    # gl "What's up, Twig. Let's go play some games."
    gl "¿Qué tal, Twig? Vamos a jugar un rato."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/IzzyDates/izzyarcadedate.rpy:36
translate spanish izzyarcadedatestart_605a4d9f:

    # gl "Hey, this place is pretty cool. I bet Stanley and Paul would love it."
    gl "Oye, este sitio mola bastante. Seguro que a Stanley y a Paul les encantaría."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/IzzyDates/izzyarcadedate.rpy:37
translate spanish izzyarcadedatestart_b1581a15:

    # gl "Maybe we could bring them sometime, when I'm able to."
    gl "Quizá podríamos traerlos algún día, cuando pueda."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/IzzyDates/izzyarcadedate.rpy:38
translate spanish izzyarcadedatestart_8de112f2:

    # pc "Yeah for sure, that sounds fun."
    pc "Sí, claro, suena divertido."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/IzzyDates/izzyarcadedate.rpy:45
translate spanish izzyarcadedatestart_f9357be7:

    # "We play games and chat for a while."
    "Jugamos y charlamos un rato."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/IzzyDates/izzyarcadedate.rpy:49
translate spanish izzyarcadedatestart_66506ca5:

    # "We try out a few different games."
    "Probamos varios juegos diferentes."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/IzzyDates/izzyarcadedate.rpy:57
translate spanish izzyarcadedatestart_726fbd6c:

    # "It's all fun and she seems to have a good time."
    "Todo es divertido y ella parece pasárselo bien."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/IzzyDates/izzyarcadedate.rpy:59
translate spanish izzyarcadedatestart_84d584ed:

    # "When we're done playing, I drive Izzy back to her house."
    "Cuando terminamos de jugar, llevo a Izzy de vuelta a su casa."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/IzzyDates/izzyarcadedate.rpy:60
translate spanish izzyarcadedatestart_2a5b6b89:

    # "I pull into her driveway and she turns to look at me."
    "Entro en su camino de acceso y ella se gira para mirarme."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/IzzyDates/izzyarcadedate.rpy:62
translate spanish izzyarcadedatestart_6dd86d8c:

    # gl "So, do you want to come inside and fuck a little?"
    gl "Bueno, ¿quieres entrar y echar un polvo?"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/IzzyDates/izzyarcadedate.rpy:69
translate spanish izzyarcadedatestart_dcbc938c:

    # gl "Cool, let's go."
    gl "Genial, vamos."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/IzzyDates/izzyarcadedate.rpy:72
translate spanish izzyarcadedatestart_dcbc938c_1:

    # gl "Cool, let's go."
    gl "Genial, vamos."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/IzzyDates/izzyarcadedate.rpy:75
translate spanish izzyarcadedatestart_7c186cf5:

    # gl "Damn. Well thanks for hanging out anyway. It was fun."
    gl "Joder. Bueno, gracias por pasar el rato de todos modos. Ha sido divertido."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/IzzyDates/izzyarcadedate.rpy:76
translate spanish izzyarcadedatestart_63fc4244:

    # pc "Bye, Izzy."
    pc "Adiós, Izzy."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/IzzyDates/izzyarcadedate.rpy:79
translate spanish izzyarcadedatestart_8b93ebfd:

    # "I wait until she gets out and walks into her house before I drive away."
    "Espero a que salga y entre en su casa antes de marcharme."

